lead_paragraph: Even if Louisville quarterback Lamar Jackson wins the Heisman Trophy in a landslide vote, there may still be a slew of finalists at the award presentation in New York on Dec. 10.

headline.print_headline: AP HEISMAN WATCH: Jackson Leads; Race for 2nd Is Crowded
